data.description:
Located in the desirable River Vista Subdivision, this delightful home is gearing up to welcome a new family. With 3 cozy bedrooms and 2 bathrooms on the upper floor, this home is tailor-made for your family's comfort.

Step inside to find an open kitchen/dining area and a welcoming living room upstairs, perfect for family gatherings and everyday joy. Need your own space? The finished den downstairs offers just that. Plus, there's a versatile office/craft room that could easily transform into an extra bedroom with the right approvals.

Inside, this home shines with fresh paint, modern flooring, and updated appliances, blending style with practicality. Outside, the house sits on a spacious, level to sloping lot, offering ample room for play and relaxation. And the best part? An extra adjoining lot of .72 acres comes with the package, giving you even more outdoor space. 1.2 acres in all!

Nature enthusiasts will appreciate the nearby river, creating a serene backdrop for your family adventures. Plus, with easy access to Sevierville and Knoxville, you're never far from city life and exciting activities.

Ideal for a large or growing family, this home is a gem waiting for its new owners. Don't miss this opportunity! Schedule your visit and start imagining the wonderful moments your family will share in this special Sevier County home. 

** Buyers and Buyers Agents to verify all information **
